put - update/replace
patch - update / modify

If record exist - update/replace
If record does not exist - will create user
All fields need to be sent even for a single field change

{
    "Name": "Jagadish",
    "Phone": 6503451789,
    "Address": "California"
}

In Patch, only the property that needs to be replaced/updates is specified

{
    "Address": "Oregon"
}